# Normalize line endings: store text as LF in the repo and check out as LF on
# every platform. Without this, core.autocrlf=true rewrites text files to CRLF
# in the working tree on Windows, and prettier (endOfLine: lf) flags every CR
# as a "Delete ␍" error. Enforcing LF here is the durable fix.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets git must never touch (line-ending normalization off).
*.png  binary
*.jpg  binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif  binary
*.ico  binary
*.webp binary
*.avif binary
*.woff  binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf   binary
*.eot   binary
